description:
Want to send Transactional Email (i.e. notification email)? Use AlphMail! Just sign up for an account at http://amail.io/ (it's free) and start sending after 5 minutes! What's great about AlphaMail is that you store your templates in our cloud, instead of bloating your code. So it's dead-easy to maintain, whenever or wherever you are.

Example code:

            IEmailService emailService = new AlphaMailEmailService()
                .SetServiceUrl("http://api.amail.io/v1/")
                .SetApiToken("ABC-DEF"); // Your AlphaMail API-token

            var message = new HelloWorldMessage()
            {
                Message = "Hello world like a boss!",
                SomeOtherMessage = "And to the rest of the world! Chíkmàa! مرحبا! नमस्ते! Dumelang!"
            };

            var payload = new EmailMessagePayload()
                .SetProjectId(12345) // ID of your AlphaMail project
                .SetSender(new EmailContact("My Company", "me@company.com")) // Sender details
                .SetReceiver(new EmailContact("John Doe", "john@doe.com")) // Receiver details
                .SetBodyObject(message);

            var response = emailService.Queue(payload);

            Console.WriteLine(response.Message);
